Pages:
- Show current status (FatCalculator);
- Show Calendar;
- Show current day;
- Show product list;

Components:
- Product (img, name, weight info);
- Portion (2 fields with number and dimension);
- Picker (to chose between different dimensions);
- Calendar (show progress);
- DayView (show products for day, add new products);
- Planner (timeline for snacks and lunch);
- Progress (eaten to all food during a day);
- Notifier (notify for upcoming snacks and lunch);
- FatCalculator (fat % according to height and weight);
- Chart (fat% over timeline);
